OL,3,CCompany fined over gardener's death
OL,4,Cwhen lawnmower fell on him
OL,6,FA gardening company has been fined
OL,7,Fover the death of an employee who was
OL,8,Fkilled when the ride-on lawnmower he
OL,9,Fwas using fell on top of him.
OL,11,FKamil Grygieniec, 23, from
OL,12,FNorthallerton, was cutting grass on a
OL,13,Fsteep bank around a pond in North
OL,14,FStanley near Ripon in October 2021
OL,15,Fwhen his mower tipped up and he ended
OL,16,Fup in the water.
OL,18,FThe Health and Safety Executive said
OL,19,Fthe mower was being used without a
OL,20,Fsafety-critical roll-over protection
OL,21,Fsystem (ROPS) fitted.
