OL,6,FAn investigation found MHS Countryside
OL,7,FManagement Limited had failed to carry
OL,8,Fout a sufficient risk assessment for
OL,9,Fthe work.
OL,11,FThe company, which is based in Bishop
OL,12,FAuckland, pleaded guilty to breaching
OL,13,Fhealth and safety laws and was fined
OL,14,F#27,000 and ordered to pay #11,166 in
OL,15,Fcosts.
OL,17,FIn a statement, Kamil's parents paid
OL,18,Ftribute to him, saying: "The pain I
OL,19,Ffeel every day since that tragedy is
OL,20,Funimaginable, I do not wish that on
OL,21,Fanybody. That day I lost part of me.
