OL,6,FHSE Inspector Darian Dundas said:
OL,7,F"This is a profoundly tragic case
OL,8,Fwhich is made all the more harrowing
OL,9,Fbecause the safety feature designed to
OL,10,Fprevent incidents like this had been
OL,11,Fremoved from the lawnmower ` leading
OL,12,Fto the fatal turn of events which has
OL,13,Frobbed a family of their loved one.
