OL,6,F"The completion of a suitable and
OL,7,Fsufficient site-specific risk
OL,8,Fassessment is vital before undertaking
OL,9,Fwork activities and ensures
OL,10,Fappropriate action can be taken to
OL,11,Feliminate hazards or, where this is
OL,12,Fnot possible, to properly control the
OL,13,Frisks.
OL,15,F"In this case, the failure to assess
OL,16,Fthe risks and ensure suitable safety
OL,17,Fmeasures were in place resulted in a
OL,18,Ftragic and entirely avoidable loss of
OL,19,Flife."
